title: Saddam's superyacht ends up as sailors' hotel
text:
Saddam's superyacht ends up as sailors' hotel Tuesday, May 22, 2018 - 01:12
This was once the presidential yacht for Saddam Hussein. this superyacht, dubbed “Basrah Breeze” was built for him in 1981, but the Iraqi dictator never boarded the 270-foot boat. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
